                            <Heading/>
                            <Paragraph>The Federal Railroad Administration (FRA) was created
                                        pursuant to section 3(e)(1) of the Department of
                                        Transportation Act of 1966 (49 U.S.C. 103).</Paragraph>
                        </Detail>
                        <Detail SortOrder="2" TypeOfProgramAndActivitiesDetailsId="3249">
